": ""}, {"cid": 2279148, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 438322, "reply_to": 2279146, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 并不会啊", "timestamp": 1628950084, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2279150, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 438322, "reply_to": 2279144, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 小便池翻台率高", "timestamp": 1628950118, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2279164, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 438322, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "减少偷拍", "timestamp": 1628950246, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2279167, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 438322, "reply_to": 2279164, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 好问题", "timestamp": 1628950284, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2279191, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 438322, "reply_to": 2279133, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 理论上来说这样是最方便的，但是会不会有优待男性的嫌疑呢？单独的小便房也可以理解为专为男性而设置的。。。", "timestamp": 1628950426, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2279204, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 438322, "reply_to": 2279191, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 并不会，只要调整好合适的配比小便房会减少男性使用隔间进而导致隔间更多的被女性使用", "timestamp": 1628950533, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2279208, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 438322, "reply_to": 2279164, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 那我觉得防止偷拍自然有别的手段，比如安个摄像头", "timestamp": 1628950576, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2279227, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 438322, "reply_to": 2279208, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 你这个手段真有效👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻", "timestamp": 1628950802, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2279245, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 438322, "reply_to": 2279208, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 只许州官放火不许百姓点灯？", "timestamp": 1628950981, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2279275, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 438322, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果隔间的板是接地接天花板的就没法偷拍吧", "timestamp": 1628951371, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2279406, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 438322, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "千万别，不想排队上厕所", "timestamp": 1628952762, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2279424, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 438322, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不过会听到上厕所的声音比较尴尬", "timestamp": 1628952968, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2279518, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 438322, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "为了维护性别差异要付出的成本太大了，比如防止偷拍，门把手要确保都是好的，门上小广告都要保证没有不然你猜会不会被喷等等，有这钱，多修几个厕所都可以", "timestamp": 1628953734, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2279590, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 438322, "reply_to": 2279275, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 厕所隔间有缝隙主要是考虑安全和通风以及方便打扫吧，要是每间都独立的话应该还得多花不少钱在打扫和通风设施建设上", "timestamp": 1628954421, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2280059, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 438322, "reply_to": 2279275, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 对这样的隔间真的很恐惧", "timestamp": 1628959131, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2280184, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 438322, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "艹，dz和我完全想到一块去了。之前还和npy讨论过这个话题，当时提到的可能出现的问题也都在评论区出现了，xs", "timestamp": 1628961214, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2280209, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 438322, "reply_to": 2279146, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 人流量大的时候，经常出现排队现象的一般是女洗手间，除了女生本来平均用时长于男生的原因外，还有一个原因就是男生小便池的空间效率高，同样大小的空间，可以安装的小便池的数量肯定是多于可以安装隔间的数量的。所以其实将一部分空间单独隔开仅安装小便池，其他大部分空间设计成男女通用的隔间时，效率应该是最高的（特别是对女生来说，排队现象肯定会显著少于现在的男女厕所面积相等但男厕装有小便池的设计", "timestamp": 1628961724, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 9, "pid": 438322, "reply": 26, "tag": null, "text": "所以厕所分男女，相比于直接把男女厕所的时候隔间作为公用有什么好处呢（男厕所的小便池倒是可以保留毕竟可以降低一些成本）", "timestamp": 1628949789, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1628961725, "url": "", "vote": {}}}